title: 이달의소녀탐구 #485 (LOONA TV #485)
summary:
Olivia Hye prepared Slime and everyone seems to enjoy it.
0:24 -- Yves made a heart for us Orbits. Choerry makes a star. Yves puts the cover one it and calls it the house of Patrick the Star.
0:36 -- Yves tried making Spongebob but failed. She then makes a slime in the shape of the fried egg on the rice. YeoJin: "That's my meal". Others make chopsticks for her.
0:57 -- Olivia cuts the episode since she has nothing more to say.
